comments: All Technical Fouls are reviewed by League Operations.
Harris (PHI) wraps his arm around Tatum's (BOS) side without removing his hand and affects his FOM.
Harden (PHI) reaches in and marginal contact occurs to Smart's (BOS) arm that does not affects his SQBR as he continues his path to the basket.
As Harden (PHI) receives the pass he falls to the ground, but does not roll over with possession of the ball before he releases it.
White (BOS) and Harden (PHI) both meet at the same point and marginal contact occurs as Harden receives the inbound pass.
Horford (BOS) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he moves to imminently guard an opponent.
Tucker (PHI) initiates contact as he grabs Smart's (BOS) arm, as he gathers ad enters his upward shooting motion, affecting his driving shot attempt.
Tucker (PHI) legally contests Horford's (BOS) jump shot attempt.
Williams (BOS) commits a take foul on Harden (PHI).
Maxey (PHI) steps out of bounds while still in possession of the ball.  Any contact from White (BOS) is marginal.

As Maxey (PHI) receives the inbound pass White (BOS) places and then immediately removes his hand from Maxey's body and very marginal contact occurs. Maxey's reaction is not consisitent with the level of contact.
Horford (BOS) dislodges Embiid (PHI) from his rebounding position, which affects his ability to pursue the loose ball.
Maxey (PHI) swipes down and initiates contact with Smart's (BOS) arm, during his driving shot attempt.
Replay review of the foul called on Tucker (PHI) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed successful and the call on the floor was overturned.
Melton (PHI) places and then immediately removes his hand from Smart's (BOS) lower body while defending around the screen. Smart's reaction is not consistent with the level of contact.
Tatum (BOS) establishes himself in Melton's (PHI) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Harris (PHI) goes to, not through, White's (BOS) space and marginal contact occurs as the two come together off-ball.
Williams (BOS) extends his arm arm forward to contest the pass attempt. Embiid (PHI) reaches out and grabs Williams' (BOS) arm and affects his ability to defend.
Harris (PHI) legally contests Tatum's (BOS) jump shot attempt.
